Give your loved ones the best gift there is: good food! Whether it's for a birthday, as a thank you or just because, treat them to a Takeaway.com gift card so they can have their favorite food delivered right to their front door. It is our mission to make everyone happy and we prefer to do that every day. In Belgium we work with more than 3500 restaurants, so from pizza to sushi and from burgers to burritos, everything is on the menu.